wgInfoModule.name: wgInfoModule
wgInfoModule.contactinfo: Ella Yu WatchGuard Technologies, Inc. 1841 Zanker Road San Jose, CA 95112 USA 408-519-4888 ella.yu@watchguard.com
wgInfoModule.description: The MIB module describes various system statistics information of WatchGuard system.

wgSystemStatisticsMIB.name: wgSystemStatisticsMIB
wgSystemStatisticsMIB.description: This is the base system information for all system related statistical counters.

wgSystemCpuUtil.name: wgSystemCpuUtil
wgSystemCpuUtil.description: CPU utilization of the system in last 5 seconds. The value is measured in 0.01%. For example, if the value is 234, then CPU utilization is 2.34%.

wgSystemTotalSendBytes.name: wgSystemTotalSendBytes
wgSystemTotalSendBytes.description: The total number of bytes sent since system is up. This number includes both cut through traffic and host traffic.

wgSystemTotalRecvBytes.name: wgSystemTotalRecvBytes
wgSystemTotalRecvBytes.description: The total number of bytes received since system is up. This number includes both cut through traffic and host traffic.

wgSystemTotalSendPackets.name: wgSystemTotalSendPackets
wgSystemTotalSendPackets.description: The total number of the packets sent since system is up. This number includes both cut through traffic and host traffic.

wgSystemTotalRecvPackets.name: wgSystemTotalRecvPackets
wgSystemTotalRecvPackets.description: The total number of the packets received since system is up. The number includes both cut through traffic and host traffic.

wgSystemStreamReqTotal.name: wgSystemStreamReqTotal
wgSystemStreamReqTotal.description: The total number of the connection requests since system is up.

wgSystemStreamReqDrop.name: wgSystemStreamReqDrop
wgSystemStreamReqDrop.description: The total number of the connection requests being dropped since system is up.

wgSystemCpuUtil1.name: wgSystemCpuUtil1
wgSystemCpuUtil1.description: CPU utilization of the system in last 1 minute. The value is measured in 0.01%. For example, if the value is 234, then CPU utilization is 2.34%.

wgSystemCpuUtil5.name: wgSystemCpuUtil5
wgSystemCpuUtil5.description: CPU utilization of the system in last 5 minutes. The value is measured in 0.01%. For example, if the value is 234, then CPU utilization is 2.34%.

wgSystemCpuUtil15.name: wgSystemCpuUtil15
wgSystemCpuUtil15.description: CPU utilization of the system in last 15 minutes. The value is measured in 0.01%. For example, if the value is 234, then CPU utilization is 2.34%.

wgSystemCurrActiveConns.name: wgSystemCurrActiveConns
wgSystemCurrActiveConns.description: Total number of currently active connections of the system.
